65
00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:00.239
So instead of 
#blacklivesmatter

66
00:03:00.239 --> 00:03:03.143
(which still rocks
but is less accessible)

67
00:03:03.143 --> 00:03:08.118
but #BlackLivesMatter,

68
00:03:08.118 --> 00:03:11.901
with the capital for each word
so it's more segmented,

69
00:03:11.901 --> 00:03:15.359
