78
00:03:38.875 --> 00:03:41.783
and that they're 
intended to be separate

79
00:03:41.783 --> 00:03:44.367
and it will read it
correctly, as well as if

80
00:03:44.367 --> 00:03:46.319
it's all lowercase
it just assumes

81
00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:49.360
