00:04:22.754 --> 00:04:25.127
use clapping hands
lots clapping hands

94
00:04:25.127 --> 00:04:27.440
of clapping hands emojis
clapping hands,"

95
00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:31.600
which doesn't really
